result.name: Tanaka

reviews.text:
Food is good quality and tasty!
Actually the size is quite big! The price are reasonable!

Normally, there are many people waiting outside for dinner, but this time we had our dinner at 9 when is no need to wait!

We order 4 items which cost only 184 Hong Kong dollars only!

Fantastic portions and taste. Especially the Chirashi-don or sashimi-don for its price, I really like that the portions were really big since I am a big eater myself. It will get crowded during certain meal hours but if you come during off-peak hours, you are good to go.

I also appreciate that some of the staff do speak English and quite fluent too. Really good service from them as well. I would definitely come back here again if I were to be in the area in future.
Budget sushi, you're paying 1.5 times of money but receiving 2-3 times amount of food here. Amazingly it was not crowded while I was there.
Very bad and below standard quality. The only selling point is the size of each sushi is big. Not recommended and no next time
Good deal sushi for average quality. The size is a bonus!

抵食夾大件，人多可以叫多d，兩個人就最好就住，咪做大嘥鬼！
食物新鮮 ，食物種類颇多，價錢合理， 七點前攞位比較好， 七點後多人排隊
出品有水準，上菜快。，因限時及提早點菜，小心點得太多太多
